snippet.title: SWOW Showcase 2021
snippet.description:
Hey all! I made a little showcase for ya! T


A little thing for you all to enjoy! I just threw a bunch of things together. I've been working hard on this little adventure :D. Hope you all like it!




If you would like to know more and see the inner workings of this project or want to join a nice discord community you can do so here!
https://discord.gg/3FzjZfWuhH




SWOW is supported by Creator's Network, a community that supports creative productions. If you are a mod author in need of personnel or someone looking to help out on a mod being developed, join at the following link: https://discord.gg/WDKPEkv57t


Love the theme? The music is by David Tregoning Check him out here!
https://www.youtube.com/user/dave1malevolus




















Disclaimer: I claim no rights to any of this. I do not, will not, nor have I accepted any form of money of any kind for my work or anything related to this project. I am not an affiliate of anything or anyone. This is a visual art experience as well as a portfolio piece I have made to demonstrate my skill set! And this is 100% just for fun. :D
